@DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5062

### Health
GET {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Text action — summarize
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "summarize",
  "text": "Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) is a technique where a language model retrieves relevant documents from an external knowledge base and uses them as context to generate grounded answers, reducing hallucination."
}

### Text action — translate (with language)
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "translate",
  "text": "Good morning, how are you?",
  "targetLanguage": "Spanish"
}

### Text action — translate without language (expect 400)
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "translate",
  "text": "Good morning, how are you?"
}

### Text action — grammar
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "grammar",
  "text": "he go to school evryday and play footbal with his freinds"
}

### Text action — answer (general, no page URL)
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "answer",
  "text": "What is the capital of France?"
}

### Text action — answer (grounded; use a URL you've already processed)
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "answer",
  "text": "What is this page about?",
  "pageUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morris_Park_Aerodrome"
}

### Text action — unknown action (expect 400)
POST {{DistributedRag.Api_HostAddress}}/api/text-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "translateinator",
  "text": "hello"
}

###
